    <item>
      <title>瑞安航空因与“盗版”网站的斗争而降低利润预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/ryanair-lowers-profit-guidance-on-fuel-costs-online-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空控股公司表示，与所谓“盗版”网站的斗争正在损害利润，因为这家折扣航空公司降低了票价以保持飞机满员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/ryanair-lowers-profit-guidance-on-fuel-costs-online-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 06:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独立袭击加剧中东紧张局势后油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东发生多起袭击事件，导致驻约旦美军死亡，红海一艘油轮被击中，导致该地区紧张局势升级，该地区约占全球原油产量的三分之一，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-29</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市在充满事件的一周中谨慎开局：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/asia-shares-set-to-gain-oil-may-rise-amid-attacks-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周市场开盘持谨慎态度，投资者准备好等待央行最新的利率前景，并做好迎接大量财报的准备。中东紧张局势升级，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/asia-shares-set-to-gain-oil-may-rise-amid-attacks-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 22:20:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Paper 称瑞士宝盛将减记 4.6 亿美元 Benko</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/julius-baer-to-announce-benko-related-write-off-soz-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Sonntagszeitung 报道，瑞士宝盛集团 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 将冲销约 4 亿瑞士法郎（合 4.63 亿美元）或更多与其破产房地产大亨雷内·本科 (Rene Benko) 的西尼亚帝国 (Signa Empire) 相关的风险敞口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/julius-baer-to-announce-benko-related-write-off-soz-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 09:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
